       Name: Cloak:flaming
       Kind: Spell
     Target: TAR_CHAR_DEFENSIVE
   Position: POS_STANDING
   Min Mana: 750
 Wait Beats: 12
 Can Learn: FALSE
Noun Damage: None
   Wear-Off: @@NThe @@ecloak@@N around your body fades.
Acquisition:
   - Sorcerer: level 48
Description:
   Cloak:flaming is the Sorcerer's signature remort cloak. It wraps the
   caster in a cloak of searing flame. When the caster takes physical damage,
   the cloak erupts and reflects 15% of the incoming damage back at the
   attacker as fire-element damage.

   The reflected damage bypasses reflection and absorption effects (it carries
   NO_REFLECT and NO_ABSORB flags). The cloak only triggers against physical
   attacks -- spells and non-physical damage do not activate it.

   For a similar effect against non-physical damage, see cloak:elements
   (Wizard).

   Duration scales with pseudo-level (pseudo_level / 8 rounds).
*******************************************************************************
